---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Company Companion — LeadFair"
  description="A custom AI chatbot trained on your business. Answers customer questions, explains your services, and captures leads on your website."
  headline="Your Business, Always Available"
  subheadline="A custom AI chatbot that lives on your website, trained on everything about your business. It answers questions, explains services, and captures leads — even when you're not around."
  accentColor="primary"
>
  <!-- What It Does -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">What the Company Companion Does</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">Think of it as the most knowledgeable employee you've ever had — who never sleeps.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Answers Customer Questions</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Trained on your services, pricing, policies, and FAQs. Customers get instant, accurate answers without waiting for you to reply.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Captures Leads</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">When a visitor is interested, the companion collects their name, contact info, and what they're looking for — and sends it to you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Explains Your Services</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Goes beyond a static FAQ. The AI can walk customers through your offerings, help them pick the right one, and explain the process.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Learns Your Voice</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">We train it to match your brand's tone — professional, friendly, casual, whatever fits. It doesn't sound like a generic bot.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Lives on Your Website</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Drops onto your site with a single line of code. Works on any website platform — Wix, WordPress, Squarespace, or custom.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Improves Over Time</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">We review conversation logs and fine-tune responses. The more customers ask, the smarter it gets.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-14">How We Set It Up</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shrink-0">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Gather Your Knowledge</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">We collect your business info, services, FAQs, policies, and anything else customers ask about. If you have a website, we can pull from that too.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shrink-0">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Train & Customize</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">We build the AI with your knowledge base and customize the tone, appearance, and behavior to match your brand.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shrink-0">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Deploy & Monitor</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">We add it to your website and monitor conversations. When customers ask new questions, we update the training to keep it accurate.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who It's For -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-14">Who This Is For</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          <p class="text-text-light">Businesses that get the same questions over and over</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          <p class="text-text-light">Service businesses with complex offerings to explain</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          <p class="text-text-light">Anyone who wants to capture leads from website visitors</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          <p class="text-text-light">Companies that want 24/7 customer support without hiring</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
